{"tid":2305040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡一名初生嬰兒驗出有新冠抗體","createTime":"2020-11-29T10:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T16:02:35.000Z","uid":278587,"like":481,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":135,"replies":[{"pid":"f84d825d4222423bbb0f2fe42029f57cbd8a8f72","tid":2305040,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=414725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414725&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=f0a373c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414725&h=fff8472b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=414725</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】新加坡一名確診感染新冠病毒的孕婦，誕下的嬰兒驗出帶有病毒抗體。<br />\n<br />\n《海峽時報》報道，這名31歲孕婦今年三月在懷孕約十星期時，與家人到歐洲旅遊，回國後證實感染新冠病毒，由於病情較輕，留醫兩個多星期出院。她到今個月初誕下兒子，驗測發現嬰兒帶有病毒抗體，醫生懷疑病毒抗體是經母體傳給胎兒。<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織表示至今仍然未知，孕婦是否會將新冠病毒傳染給胎兒，至今亦沒在羊水或母乳內，發現新冠活病毒。美國醫學協會期刊刊登的報告亦指，孕婦將新冠病毒傳給胎兒的情況很罕見。"},{"pid":"8cacf4b72629d786bf251aaeb9d760872b81efff","tid":2305040,"uid":275238,"like":349,"dislike":2,"score":347,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"x-men新紀元"},{"pid":"44208563bfcd235c4481c3666f8c24e74aec3b5a","tid":2305040,"uid":155095,"like":277,"dislike":2,"score":275,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"新人類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d7bffd630602281faf876fc31475239fea289e","tid":2305040,"uid":121546,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"新人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8f907cfd5e6e271510c1cbd16258d8b6644f22","tid":2305040,"uid":25316,"like":94,"dislike":3,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"Newtype<img src=\"/assets/faces/m