25\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414725&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=f0a373c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414725&h=fff8472b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=414725</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】新加坡一名確診感染新冠病毒的孕婦，誕下的嬰兒驗出帶有病毒抗體。<br />\n<br />\n《海峽時報》報道，這名31歲孕婦今年三月在懷孕約十星期時，與家人到歐洲旅遊，回國後證實感染新冠病毒，由於病情較輕，留醫兩個多星期出院。她到今個月初誕下兒子，驗測發現嬰兒帶有病毒抗體，醫生懷疑病毒抗體是經母體傳給胎兒。<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織表示至今仍然未知，孕婦是否會將新冠病毒傳染給胎兒，至今亦沒在羊水或母乳內，發現新冠活病毒。美國醫學協會期刊刊登的報告亦指，孕婦將新冠病毒傳給胎兒的情況很罕見。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"要捉去食住人奶學國安法<br />\n致新人類：國安大法好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8a8db15992faf314c70473c44c0f1da1d6f791","tid":2305040,"uid":60814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8cacf4b72629d786bf251aaeb9d760872b81efff","tid":2305040,"uid":275238,"like":349,"dislike":2,"score":347,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"x-men新紀元"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:04:57.000Z","msg":"x-monkey<br />\n<br />\n猿人新世紀"},{"pid":"44740f67bf74ec4ee79d8537ac16c55b7955ae50","tid":2305040,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"有抗體係代表傳染咗比佢下話..."},{"pid":"a56984f91ff5cfad45e47d554239a1b94debea33","tid":2305040,"uid":68840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"三月?&nbsp;即係歐洲開始爆到仆街果段時間?"},{"pid":"fd2b28c3ef43293b1d507343bdb39834e8b7a4ea","tid":2305040,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"猩猩有愛滋抗體<br />\nmonkey有武肺抗體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89bc760a1ce2706a3d351aacee3e50691c693cb","tid":2305040,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":